  "texts": [
    "It can be verified that LOADF achieves O(N) spacetime allocation: the only steps where O(N) ancillae are active are the rotation gates (depth O(1)) and the uncopying step that follows.",
    "However, the uncopying step for O(N) qubits was seen in Figs.",
    "18 and 12 to occupy only O(N) spacetime allocation.",
    "Unless labeled otherwise, all ancilla qubits begin and end with the |0⟩ states.",
    "We also note that register B can be mostly allocated with dirty qubits |φ O(N) ⟩ [16] instead of qubits in the |0⟩ states."
  ],
